        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Using your occult connections and incredible powers of persuasion, you convince yourself that the triggering damage is a figment of your imagination. The damage changes from its usual damage type to mental damage, and the damaging effect gains the nonlethal trait. You can\u2019t use this reaction if you are immune to mental effects or mental damage.",
